Transcription.Text: Her thoughts at this moment were chaotic. The coach now turned in another direction, towards the wild and desolate region behind the baths. It was sparsely inhabited, dotted with fallow fields and terraced vineyards, and here and there jutted a brown outcrop of flower-wreathed ruins.
